<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="under-prep">under <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ʌndə(r)/    美 /'ʌndər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在...下面</strong></h4>
<p>反 over </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t stand under a tree during a thunderstorm.
雷雨时不要站在树下。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He got out from under the bed. 
他从床底下钻出来了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>低于；少于；在...以下：</strong></h4>
<p>反 over </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Nearly l8 million children <strong>under the age of</strong> five around the world are estimated to be overweight.
估计全世界有近1800万5岁以下的儿童超重。</p><footer>2013 湖北改</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>在...之下：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>work under sb
在某人的领导下工作</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>under control / pressure</strong>
在掌控之下/在压力下</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>在...中：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>under construction / repair 
在建设/修理中</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is still <strong>under discussion</strong> (= being discussed) whether the old bus station should be replaced with a modern hotel or not. 
是否应拆掉旧车站建一个现代化的宾馆还在讨论中。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>用；凭借：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mary Ann Evans wrote <strong>under</strong> <strong>the</strong> <strong>name</strong> <strong>of</strong> George Eliot. 
玛丽·安·埃文斯用乔治·艾略特作笔名进行创作。</p></div></div>